column2: "This guy is definitely saying hello, too!"
"After I ran into you before, I kept communicating with them."
"I can't understand them completely, but I've started to pick up the basics."
"Still, it seems like depending on the tone, the meaning changes, so it's going to take a while."
"Yes, I know. As long as I understand by feeling, then it's okay."
"I know, I know... It's not very cast-like of me to say something like that."
